    "description": "Sneebles The Half Cat is a fast-paced, white-knuckle retro style arcade game. Help Sneebles protect his burrito from mysterious giant tomatoes that are trying to destroy it. Where did they come from? Will Sneebles ever get a chance to eat his burrito? Find out as you unlock achievements and work toward new high scores!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Featuring</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Precision gameplay with a focus on chain building to rack up big points.<br></li><li>Seven unique magic drops to assist you, including five different power-ups.<br></li><li>31 in-game achievements.<br></li><li>An interactive tutorial.<br></li><li>Stylized pixel art inspired by the 16-bit era.<br></li><li>A dynamic soundtrack composed in the style of 16-bit to match.<br></li><li>Expressive characters and animations.<br></li><li>An unlockable full-length short cartoon inspired by 90s cartoons (presented in the style of 90s video game cutscenes!)</li></ul>",
